    "causal_summary": "The 028 deep review (tri-model 40-seat fan-out plus a 10-iteration lens deep-dive, claude adversarially verified) closed with a NOT CONVERGED verdict: 0 P0, 6 confirmed P1 and 91 P2. The single blocking class is benchmark fidelity, where the per-flag eval driver measures every flag on a non-representative all-channels path so the criterion-4 flip decision rests on the wrong data. Two concurrency races, one schema identity split and a shipped-doc mislabel round out the P1 set. The findings need a bounded, per-family remediation plan so each fix has a clear target, a quoted source finding and an explicit verification contract.",
